    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-求最大值"><a href="#1-求最大值" class="headerlink" title="1.求最大值"></a>1.求最大值</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>有3个整数a,b,c，由键盘输入，输出其中最大的数(用if-else语句或条件表达式)</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:   a b c</strong></p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>max</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>1 2 3</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>3</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> a, b, c;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, &amp;a, &amp;b, &amp;c);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (a&gt;b &amp;&amp; a&gt;c)	</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, a);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (b &gt; a &amp;&amp; b &gt; c)</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, a);</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, c);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="错误用法"><a href="#错误用法" class="headerlink" title="错误用法"></a>错误用法</h3><p>由于时间的关系写的很匆忙，出了写问题，在写if…else语句的时候需要注意花括号的位置。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (b + c &lt; a)</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"不能构成三角形\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	  <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">	   <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%.3lf"</span>, S);</span><br><span class="line">	  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>注意到了吗？本属于 <a href="">printf</a>的花括号被else抢去了。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="2-分段函数"><a href="#2-分段函数" class="headerlink" title="2.分段函数"></a>2.分段函数</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>有一个函数：</p>
<p><img src="https://edu-image.nosdn.127.net/4ABFEDE6F4152C0F6E492702B2AD94DE.png?imageView&thumbnail=890x0&quality=100" alt="img"></p>
<p>编写一个C程序，输入x的值，输出y相应的值</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:</strong>   x</p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>y</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>5</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>9</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> a;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;a);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">10</span>)a = <span class="number">3</span> * a - <span class="number">11</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">1</span>)a = <span class="number">2</span> * a - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, a);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="遗留问题"><a href="#遗留问题" class="headerlink" title="遗留问题"></a>遗留问题</h3><p>在下述代码里</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">1</span>)a = <span class="number">2</span> * a - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>本来我是这样写的</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		 a = (a &lt; <span class="number">1</span>) ? a : a = <span class="number">2</span> * a - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>但是编译器却提醒我表达式左侧必须是可修改的左值，经过一番查找，还是不能发问题，结果发现上面的代码更加简单。等我我想好了在来这里补充吧。</p>
<h4 id="补充："><a href="#补充：" class="headerlink" title="补充："></a>补充：</h4><p>改</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = (a &lt; <span class="number">1</span>) ? a :<span class="number">2</span> * a - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>出的问题是：我在前边已经有了‘a =’也就是a被某个数赋值，但是我后面又写了 a = 2 * a - 1，于是就成了这样：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a &#x3D; a &#x3D; 2 * a - 1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>所以，最初的想法的话，完整的，正确的，写法是：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> a;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;a);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">10</span>)a = <span class="number">3</span> * a - <span class="number">11</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		a = (a &lt; <span class="number">1</span>) ? a : <span class="number">2</span> * a - <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, a);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>最后发现还不如最开始简练。</strong></p>
<h2 id="3-成绩等级"><a href="#3-成绩等级" class="headerlink" title="3.成绩等级"></a>3.成绩等级</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>给出一百分制成绩，要求输出成绩等级’A’、’B’、’C’、’D’、’E’。90分以上为‘A’,80<del>89为‘B’,70</del>79为‘C’,60~69为‘D’, 60分以下为‘E’。</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:</strong>   成绩(0-100)</p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>成绩等级</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>95</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>A</p>
<p><strong>猜测</strong>：第一反应使用switch语句，但是100分有一百个数，想来比较麻烦，还是if…else大法好了。</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> a;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">char</span> b;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;a);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &lt; <span class="number">60</span>)b = <span class="string">'E'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	  <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">90</span>)b = <span class="string">'A'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">80</span>)b = <span class="string">'B'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">			&#123;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt;= <span class="number">70</span>)b = <span class="string">'C'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">else</span> b = <span class="string">'D'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%c"</span>,b);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="4-二元一次方程"><a href="#4-二元一次方程" class="headerlink" title="4.二元一次方程"></a>4.二元一次方程</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>编写程序，从键盘输入一个二元一次方程ax^2+bx+c=0的三个参数a、b、c（均为整数），求此方程的实根。如果方程有实根，则输出实根（精确到小数点后2位，较大实根在前），如果没有实根，则输出”方程没有实根”。</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:</strong>a b c</p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>x1 x2</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>1 4 3</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>-1.00 -3.00</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;math.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">double</span> a, b, c, disc, x1, x2, p, q;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%lf %lf %lf"</span>, &amp;a, &amp;b, &amp;c);</span><br><span class="line">	disc = b * b - <span class="number">4</span> * a * c;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (disc &lt; <span class="number">0</span>)<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"方程没有实根"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		p = -b / (<span class="number">2.0</span> * a);</span><br><span class="line">		q = <span class="built_in">sqrt</span>(disc) / (<span class="number">2.0</span> * a);</span><br><span class="line">		x1 = p + q;</span><br><span class="line">		x2 = p - q;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (x1 &gt; x2)<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%.2lf %.2lf"</span>,x1,x2);</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%.2lf %.2lf"</span>, x2, x1);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;		</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这里是改编了书上84页的代码。</p>
<h2 id="5-递减序列"><a href="#5-递减序列" class="headerlink" title="5.递减序列"></a>5.递减序列</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>编写一个程序，从键盘依次读入5个实数，如果整个输入序列不递减，则输出YES，否则输出NO.</p>
<p> （所谓输入序列不递减，指对于序列中连续的两个数n1和n2，满足n1&lt;=n2）</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:</strong>n1 n2 n3 n4 n5</p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>YES/NO</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>5 4 3 2 1</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>NO</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> n1, n2, n3, n4, n5;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d %d %d"</span>,&amp;n1,&amp;n2,&amp;n3,&amp;n4,&amp;n5);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (n1&lt;=n2||n2&lt;=n3||n3&lt;=n4||n4&lt;=n5) </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"YES"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"NO"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="6-判断闰年"><a href="#6-判断闰年" class="headerlink" title="6.判断闰年"></a>6.判断闰年</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>写一个程序判断某一年是否为闰年</p>
<p>(①普通年能整除4且不能整除100的为闰年.(如2004年就是闰年,1901年不是闰年)②世纪年能整除400的是闰年.(如2000年是闰年,1900年不是闰年))</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:</strong>年份</p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>xx is a leap year    或     xx is not a leap year</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>2001</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>2001 is not a leap year</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> Y;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d"</span>, &amp;Y);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (Y % <span class="number">400</span> == <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d is a leap year"</span>, Y);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (Y % <span class="number">4</span> == <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; Y % <span class="number">100</span> != <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d is a leap year"</span>, Y);</span><br><span class="line">		    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">		    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d is not a leap year"</span>, Y);</span><br><span class="line">		    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="注意"><a href="#注意" class="headerlink" title="注意"></a>注意</h3><p>1.在写 if (Y % 400 == 0) 时，最开始我写的是 if (Y % 400 = 0)，编译器这里再次提醒我表达式必须是可修改左值，当我将‘=’改为’==’就好了，这是因为，在c语言里，’=’表示赋值，而’==’才表示赋值。</p>
<p>2.最开始我的代码是这样的：</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (Y % <span class="number">400</span> == <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d is a leap year"</span>, Y);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (Y % <span class="number">4</span> == <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; Y % <span class="number">100</span> != <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d is a leap year"</span>, Y);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d is not a leap year"</span>, Y);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这里注意，如果没有else，在执行一个if后会继续执行下一个if，在这里，每次三个都会执行，不仅不正确，还降低了效率。当输入400时，结果为：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">400 is a leap year400 is not a leap year</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="7-排序"><a href="#7-排序" class="headerlink" title="7.排序"></a>7.排序</h2><p><strong>题目内容：</strong></p>
<p>输入三个整数a,b,c，从小到大排列依次存入a,b,c中并输出。</p>
<p><strong>输入格式:</strong>a b c</p>
<p><strong>输出格式：</strong>由小到大排序后的a b c</p>
<p><strong>输入样例：</strong>3 1 5</p>
<p><strong>输出样例：</strong>1 3 5</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span><span class="comment">//题目要求是从小到大，由于我是按从大到小来写的，就改一下，读起来可能有点混乱</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> a,b,c;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, &amp;a,&amp;b,&amp;c);</span><br><span class="line">	</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt; b) </span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		 <span class="keyword">if</span> (b &gt; c) <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, c, b, a);  <span class="comment">// a最大</span></span><br><span class="line">		 <span class="keyword">else</span>   <span class="comment">//a&gt;b c&gt;b</span></span><br><span class="line">		 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			 <span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt; c) <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, b, c, a);</span><br><span class="line">			 &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			 <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, b, a, c);  </span><br><span class="line">			 &#125;</span><br><span class="line">			</span><br><span class="line">		 &#125;</span><br><span class="line">		</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">else</span>  <span class="comment">//a&lt;b</span></span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span> (a &gt; c)<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, c, a, b);</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="comment">//a&lt;b a&lt;c</span></span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (b &gt; c)<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, a, c, b);</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">else</span><span class="comment">//a&lt;b b&lt;c a&lt;c</span></span><br><span class="line">			&#123;			</span><br><span class="line">					<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"%d %d %d"</span>, a, b, c);</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;			</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>我常常认为编程题都很好玩，现在也是这么认为，因为计算机解决了人们最麻烦最棘手的问题——计算，使得我们能够花更多的时间精力去思考问题的方法。今天的题并不难这些题有着各种各样的方法可以去实现，上节课所讲的知识很多我也没有用上，如switch语句，由于时间关系，直接用了简单粗暴的if…else语句了。</p>
